Open Source FPV Frame Version 0.1
The SOURCE MICRO is a collaborative open source project
initiated by Team Blacksheep, targeted at drone enthusiasts.
It follows the footsteps of SOURCE ONE, a FPV freestyle frame.
The frame design is donated to the community to empower creators
and makers, and integrate best practices and current trends faster
into a continuously manufactured product.
It's a cheaper alternative to clones that can be bought with
the peace of mind that the big brands of the FPV industry stand for.
